title: seasalts
author: seasalts
content: One new Mining pool http://qiepool.xyz is deployed for QIE mining. It support ethash algo and two famous miner programs.Maintnet has ~190G hashrate and ~1.6T now. It is not easy to mine one coin by limited power, may someone share ethash power to mine 1 coinPool Fee is 0.1% (for payout purpose)

comments.author: seasalts
comments.body: Appreciate all donations. Some miners contribute to the pool.Bad luck or technical issue, no block found and would close the pool first.Save your power. Thanks.
